<p>For me, here&#8217;s the difference between your essays and Paul Graham&#8217;s: yours (at least this latest series, now that you&#8217;ve given up programming to become a writer) are just whinging, wrapped in a high falutin&#8217; sophomoric sophistication.</p>

<p>They&#8217;re tough to get through, and leave a bad feeling.</p>

