<p>Aaron: In any event, the fact that Bach&#8217;s music survived while that of his contemporaries didn&#8217;t may mean that Bach&#8217;s music was better, but I don&#8217;t see how it can mean that it&#8217;s better than today&#8217;s music, which hasn&#8217;t exactly died out yet.</p>

